{
  "texts": [
    "In periodontics, 27 out of 40 responses (67.5%) showed an acceptable I-CVI.",
    "The overall content validity of the responses revealed acceptable results in terms of relevance and clarity i.e., S-CVI=0.80 and 0.87 respectively.",
    "However, regarding the accuracy and up-to-date knowledge of the responses, the values were not satisfactory with S-CVI=0.77 and 0.76 respectively.",
    "Oral & Maxillofacial Surgery.",
    "In oral surgery, only 14 out of 40 responses (35%) showed an acceptable I-CVI."
  ]
}